{"tid":1325860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【和理非升級】8月多區同時遊行，終極目標18區同時遊行","createTime":"2019-07-17T04:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T04:47:19.000Z","uid":125508,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c6087a75232bf55a777c43aa7ba2e545d043bd1e","tid":1325860,"uid":125508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:17:25.000Z","msg":"728東西夾擊，無心插柳，將能夠測試兩項東西：<br />\n1. 社區動員能力：沙田遊行測試到，家居物質和街坊加入對抗爭有利，也帶來掩護。<br />\n2. 敵方布防是否疲乏，以及分散力量的成效：部分前線在內部和社交媒體發惱騷，雖然不知真假，但隨著東西夾擊，將會測試到敵方是否開始變弱。<br />\n鑒於8月暫時沒有活動，和理非可以逐步升級，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>8月開始嘗試兩區，三區同時遊行/集會。一直造勢到十一、11月24日區選，一鼓作氣。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6a9e857fad3b940f2e44bcfdfd193e7110a604e1","tid":1325860,"uid":125508,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:17:29.000Z","msg":"預計後續影響：<br />\n1. 敵方力量可能真的疲乏，然後政府要請外援，最有可能是假冒敵方的廣東武警。<br />\n2. 敵方疲乏hea做<br />\n3. 敵方倒戈<br />\n4. 因應敵方疲乏，政府可能真的下全港戒嚴令，不過因為成本大，所以機會微；因為分區行動，分局戒嚴是不可靠的，所以一下子政府的選擇只有一不做，二不休全港戒嚴。"},{"pid":"566f150a3b08df9413db05f34f1201e2777d2870","tid":1325860,"uid":125508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:18:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1858150924561ad51ab54e63ed2c85f5dcb21589","tid":1325860,"uid":125508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:18:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9defb5b50dd074df8569d5b3b6f997662607a36b","tid":1325860,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a3bd5bcfa2a77afa4b842424f570240d161d43a","tid":1325860,"uid":125508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T04:22:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad13da2571a4ff74f09c0e484af6cd54f87bc254","tid":1325860,"uid":125508,"like":0,"dislike